      {
        "block_label": "figure_title",
        "block_content": "Figure 5: The impact of sampling intervals. We train DDIM model on CIFAR-10. We find that adjusting the sampling interval has a relatively small influence in the first case and does not affect our method in the latter case. This makes our algorithm applicable to more setups.",
        "block_bbox": [
